            "title": "聯想控股午後跌近3%  去年虧轉盈賺1.33億人幣不派息",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">聯想控股(03396)午後跌，現跌2.7%，報9.01元，成交4710萬元。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">公司公布，截至2024年12月底止全年業績轉虧為盈，錄得股東應佔溢利1.33億元(人民幣．下同)，每股基本盈利0.06元，不派息。2023年度虧損38.74億元。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">期內，總收入5128.06億元，按年升17.61%。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/14811799-%e8%81%af%e6%83%b3%e6%8e%a7%e8%82%a1%e5%8d%88%e5%be%8c%e8%b7%8c%e8%bf%913-%e5%8e%bb%e5%b9%b4%e8%99%a7%e8%bd%89%e7%9b%88%e8%b3%ba1-33%e5%84%84%e4%ba%ba%e5%b9%a3%e4%b8%8d%e6%b4%be%e6%81%af",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/07/03396.jpg.webp",
            "pub_date": "2025-03-28 13:25:45",
