        },
        {
            "title": "石藥盈利跌逾25%   末期息減近27%",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">石藥(01093)公布，2024年度股東應佔溢利46.83億元(人民幣‧下同)，按年減25.4%，股東應佔每股盈利36..87分，按年跌25.5%。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：石藥集團官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/05/20240527_FI_source-web_01093-1.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：石藥集團官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/05/20240527_FI_source-web_01093-1.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">圖片來源：石藥集團官網</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">末期息10港仙，較去年同期14港仙跌28.6%，全年派息26仙，按年跌7.1%。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">成藥業務於本年度錄得收入237.36億元，較去年減少7.4%，抗腫瘤藥銷售44億元，按年減28.3%;神經系統藥物銷售96.45億元，按年升6.1%。呼吸系統藥物銷售按年跌23.1%，報11.99億元。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/14811688-%e7%9f%b3%e8%97%a5%e7%9b%88%e5%88%a9%e8%b7%8c%e9%80%be25-%e6%9c%ab%e6%9c%9f%e6%81%af%e6%b8%9b%e8%bf%9127",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/11/20241115_FI_source-web_01093.jpg.webp",
